<section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Engagement Options</h1>
  <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base text-slate-700">
    Every project is scoped case by case. We provide a clear written proposal based on your goals, timeline, and quality needs.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Discovery and Scope Plan</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-cyan-700">Custom quote</p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
        <li>- Review your goals and existing setup</li>
        <li>- Define practical build options and priorities</li>
        <li>- Clear first-step recommendation you can act on quickly</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-cyan-200 bg-cyan-50/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Website or App Build</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-cyan-700">Fixed-scope proposal</p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
        <li>- Custom website or web app</li>
        <li>- AI-assisted delivery for faster turnaround</li>
        <li>- Engineering quality checks for stability and maintainability</li>
        <li>- Practical handover and launch support</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/90 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Support and Improvements (Optional)</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-cyan-700">Ongoing plan</p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
        <li>- Ongoing updates and small improvements</li>
        <li>- Monitoring and technical maintenance</li>
        <li>- Priority support for quick fixes</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>

  <section class="mt-12 rounded-3xl border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50/80 p-6 lg:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">How we stay highly cost-competitive</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
      AI-assisted workflows reduce delivery time, and we pass that efficiency into project pricing instead of billing like traditional large agencies.
      If you already have a comparable written quote, share it with us and we will review scope, quality, and timeline to provide a competitive alternative where feasible.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Comparisons are assessed case by case and are not a blanket guarantee for every project.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-cyan-200 bg-cyan-50/80 p-6 lg:p-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Charity and non-profit support</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
      We reserve part of our delivery capacity for verified charities and non-profits, with pro-bono or heavily discounted project options where feasible.
      Support level is determined case by case based on scope, urgency, and current capacity.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
      Eligibility and offer terms are confirmed in writing before work begins. This is not an automatic or guaranteed entitlement.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="mt-10">
    <%= link_to "Get a Free Plan", "#{contact_path}#audit-form", class: "inline-flex rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-emerald-500 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:from-cyan-600 hover:to-emerald-600" %>
  </div>
</section>
